 <h1 class="hero__title">Network with a specialty infusion provider built for South Carolina.</h1>
 <p class="hero__lead">CoreFlow Specialty Infusion is a South Carolina-licensed specialty infusion pharmacy offering home infusion services as a lower-cost alternative to hospital outpatient and inpatient settings. We are pursuing URAC Specialty Pharmacy v5.0 and ACHC IRX-NO797 accreditation.</p>
 <p>To inquire about network participation or credentialing, complete the form below or contact our credentialing team directly.</p>

